description: Osiris contains 94 examples of French Horn, 46 examples of Horn (two of which are mixtures), 12 examples of Corno, 4 examples of Orchestral Horn, and 2 examples of Cor d'Orchestre. Horn 8', Swell; St. Mary the Virgin, Finedon, Northamptonshire, England; Schrider 1717. This stop may have been a later addition.
